ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: WDesigning Weimar Classicism starts with and tests the notion the Classism is a matter of design and construction. It combines aesthetics and political theory to figure out what intellectual trends and ideas unfolded in Classisism. These inquiries occur on the the basis of close readings of theoretical texts, philosophy, novellas, and lyric poetry. I would highly recommend it since it provides a great introduction to material if it is new to one and offers new ways to think about it even if one already knows some of the texts.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: The course deepened my knowldge of an important literary epoch and even more significatnly deepedn my understanding of the formation of literary periodsa and trends in general. It developed my skills in close reading and thinking about an absract problem. This course insspired some ideas about modern literature that will play a central role in my ongoing research.
